You must have emscripten via emsdk installed.

Provide
  libraylib.web.a
 from
  emmake make PLATFORM=PLATFORM_WEB BUILD_MODE=RELEASE
   in raylib/src

emmake make
emrun emancer.index

Please note that if your layout keys are not QWERTY your input will be strange, unfortunately.

Arrow keys still exist, and of course the bomb key is still X/F.
Gamepad should work.
